      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle is priced to move and ready for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character and some needed repairs! While it shows significant wear and will require some mechanical attention, it\u2019s a fantastic opportunity for a handy owner to breathe new life into a car at a very accessible price point.",
