    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and thinning clear coat on the roof. Inside, the cabin is intact but shows typical wear, including some staining on the upholstery and a cracked dashboard. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid, functional vehicle that has been used regularly and priced according to its current state.",
